AKAI Mpk mini mkII Bitwig Controller Script
===========================================

================= PROGRAM 1 ====================

### Joystick
- LEFT/RIGHT: Pitchbend
- UP/DOWN: -

### Pads CC Mode
```
Bank A                                         Bank B
|---------|---------|---------|---------|      |---------|---------|---------|---------|
| ARM     | SOLO    | MUTE    | CLIP    |      | TRACK   | DEVICE  | PADS    | TOGGLE  |
| TRACK   | TRACK   | TRACK   | OVERDUB |      | UP      | UP      | UP      | MACRO   |
|         |         |         |         |      |         |         |         |         |
|---------|---------|---------|---------|      |---------|---------|---------|---------| 
|TRANSPORT|TRANSPORT|TRANSPORT|TRANSPORT|      | TRACK   | DEVICE  | PADS    | NEXT    |
| STOP    | PLAY    | REC     | OVERDUB |      | DOWN    | DOWN    | DOWN    | DEVICE  |
|         |         |         |         |      |         |         |         |PARAMETER|
|---------|---------|---------|---------|      |---------|---------|---------|---------|
```
### Pads PROG CHANGE Mode
```
Bank A                                         Bank B
|---------|---------|---------|---------|      |---------|---------|---------|---------|
|INSPECTOR|PER-     | PROJECT | BROWSER |      | DEVICE  | DEVICE  | DEVICE  | TOGGLE  |
|         | SPECTIVE|         |         |      | PRESET  |CATEGORIE| CREATOR | MACRO   |
|         |         |         |         |      | UP      | UP      | UP      |         |
|---------|---------|---------|---------|      |---------|---------|---------|---------| 
| NOTE    | AUTO-   | MIXER   | DEVICE  |      | DEVICE  | DEVICE  | DEVICE  | NEXT    |
|         |  MATION |         |         |      | PRESET  |CATEGORIE| CREATOR | DEVICE  |
|         |         |         |         |      | DOWN    | DOWN    | DOWN    |PARAMETER|
|---------|---------|---------|---------|      |---------|---------|---------|---------|
```
### Knobs
```
  /---\     /---\     /---\     /---\
  | 1 |     | 2 |     | 3 |     | 4 |
  \---/     \---/     \---/     \---/
Device     Device    Device    Device
Macro 1    Macro 2   Macro 3   Macro 4

  /---\     /---\     /---\     /---\
  | 5 |     | 6 |     | 7 |     | 8 |
  \---/     \---/     \---/     \---/
Device     Device    Device    Device
Macro 5    Macro 6   Macro 7   Macro 8
```


================= PROGRAM 2 ====================

